NEW JERSEY TO WESTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
DNC 16, DNC 17.
1. 41 FOOT S/V WINDWARD PASSAGE, WHITE HULL
   WITH BLUE STRIPE, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
   OVERDUE JERSEY CITY (40-42.60N 074-03.60W)
   TO BERMUDA (32-21.75N 064-49.00W) OR
   BAHAMAS (25-00.00N 077-24.00W). LAST
   KNOWN POSITION IN 40-20.00N 073-45.00W AT
   050447Z NOV. VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED
   TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO US COAST GUARD ATLANTIC AREA,
   PHONE: 757 398 6700, FAX: 757 398 6775,
   E-MAIL: LANTWATCH@USCG.MIL.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2554/23.
